@allenlavoie What happens internally when I assign the same variable multiple times to self? E.g.:

({'model/embedding/.ATTRIBUTES/VARIABLE_VALUE': <tf.Variable 'embedding:0' shape=(1, 1) dtype=float32_ref>}, nodes {
  children {
    node_id: 1
    local_name: "model"
  }
}
nodes {
  children {
    node_id: 2
    local_name: "embedding"
  }
  children {
    node_id: 2
    local_name: "test"
  }
}
nodes {
  attributes {
    name: "VARIABLE_VALUE"
    full_name: "embedding"
    checkpoint_key: "model/embedding/.ATTRIBUTES/VARIABLE_VALUE"
  }
}
)
